»To commemorate the generous legacy left by Betty Jenkins (Jenks) towards the land and habitat management of Conwy Reserve in memory of Helen and Leslie Cheall of Blundellsands"Į
║In fondest memory of my husband
TREVOR PRYTHERCH JONES
of Flint
Who spent many happy years,
both working and at leisure in Llandudno.
Always in my thoughts. Your loving wife Doreen."╠
